mir zaynen dan alt, fun nayn yor nit alt geven.

00:18:44.135 --> 00:18:48.264
zogt er, "oyb emetser vet zikh gefinen aykh tsu firn

00:18:49.097 --> 00:18:51.201
vel ikh erloybn aykh tsu forn."

