iz geshtanen a kristn, un zi zogt az zi vet undz avekfirn.

00:18:55.880 --> 00:18:59.064
hot er undz gegebn a erloybenish tsu forn.

00:19:00.133 --> 00:19:04.177
UNK un azoy zaynen mir avekgeforn. dos iz geven dem ershtn

00:19:04.841 --> 00:19:05.898
APRIL

00:19:06.782 --> 00:19:09.341
nayntsn dray un tsvantsik.

00:19:10.511 --> 00:19:12.935
zaynen mir geforn tsurik in

00:19:14.308 --> 00:19:15.332
in Vilne.

00:19:15.438 --> 00:19:17.356
un s'hot genumen a vokh tsayt.

00:19:17.598 --> 00:19:20.056
dertseylt a bisl vi azoy ir hot aykh

00:19:20.602 --> 00:19:24.106
gezegnt fun zeydi un fun di tante.

00:19:25.192 --> 00:19:28.646
mir hobn zikh gezegnt mit, mit zey zeyer

00:19:29.664 --> 00:19:31.543
meynendik az mir veln zikh zen

00:19:31.543 --> 00:19:33.084
mir veln zikh nokh zen.

00:19:34.727 --> 00:19:38.991
mir hobn nit getroym- nit getroymt az s'vet kumen aza, aza fayer.

00:19:39.283 --> 00:19:45.060
un m'vet alts farnikhtn un mir veln shoyn keynem nit zen. mir hobn vegn dem afile nit geklert. ⟨zayendik⟩ kinder oyf

