hobn mir dos gedarft gebn a telegrame dem papn az er zol kumen

00:20:34.360 --> 00:20:36.180
undz opnemen tsum.

00:20:36.995 --> 00:20:38.137
di goye

00:20:38.261 --> 00:20:42.531
hot zikh tsugeganvet bay mir di gelt un gezogt az zi vet gebn aleyn di telegrame.

00:20:42.531 --> 00:20:44.831
ikh hob nit gevust az UNK zi git

00:20:44.910 --> 00:20:48.651
ikh hob gemeynt az zi hot gezogt az zi vet gebn, vet zi gebn di telegrame.

00:20:49.314 --> 00:20:51.614
mir zaynen gekumen tsu forn, iz der

00:20:51.614 --> 00:20:53.476
pape, tate nit geven.

